<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Samsung S26 Ultra</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial;
      background: #111;
      color: white;
      margin: 0;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      height: 100vh;
    }

    .card {
      display: flex;
      background: #1e1e1e;
      border-radius: 15px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
      max-width: 800px;
    }

    .card img {
      width: 350px;
      object-fit: cover;
    }

    .info {
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .info h1 {
      margin-top: 0;
      color: #00bcd4;
    }

    .info p {
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .specs {
      margin-top: 15px;
    }

    .specs li {
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="card">
  <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1511707171634-5f897ff02aa9" alt="Samsung Phone">
  <div class="info">
    <h1>Samsung S26 Ultra</h1>
    <p>Samsung S26 Ultra — bu eng yangi va kuchli flagman smartfonlardan biri. U zamonaviy dizayn, kuchli kamera va yuqori tezlikdagi ishlashi bilan ajralib turadi.</p>

    <ul class="specs">
      <li>📱 Ekran: 6.9" Dynamic AMOLED</li>
      <li>⚡ Protsessor: Exynos / Snapdragon (eng yangi)</li>
      <li>📸 Kamera: 200MP + zoom</li>
      <li>🔋 Batareya: 5000mAh</li>
      <li>💾 Xotira: 12GB / 16GB RAM</li>
      <li>📡 5G qo‘llab-quvvatlaydi</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
